<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="10Oct1921"><font color="red">10 October 1921</font>, <cite>Letters I</cite> (JJ to Robert McAlmon): Darantiere is damn slow setting <cite>Penelope</cite> &hellip; Have sent the first part of <cite>Ithaca</cite> to the typist and am working like a lunatic, trying to revise and improve and correct and continue and create all at the one time</div>
